<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="19Dec1931"><font color="red">19 December 1931</font> <i>Beach Letters</i> (to Sylvia Beach): In <i>Living Authors</i> Nicholson says he is the grandson of Archibald Hamilton Rowen, the Irish leader (from whom Richard Rowan and Archie in <i>Exiles</i> take their names. </div>
